file1.highlighted_code: def SNT(n): if n<2: return False; for i in range(2,int(n**(0.5))+1): if n%i==0: return False; return True; m,n=list(map(int,input().split())) j=-1 for i in range(n,m-1,-1): k=str(i) v=0 for p in k: v+=int(p) if SNT(v)==True: j=i break print(j)
